  "prompt": "How can I watch the Shorty Awards on TV in the US?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, the **Shorty Awards** are primarily streamed online rather than being broadcast on traditional TV networks in the United States. Here\u2019s how you can watch the Shorty Awards:\n\n1. **Official Shorty Awards Website:**\n   - **Visit**: [shortyawards.com](https://shortyawards.com/)\n   - **Details**: The official website typically provides information about the live stream, including links and viewing instructions.\n\n2. **Streaming Platforms:**\n   - **YouTube Live**: The Shorty Awards often stream the event live on their official YouTube channel. You can subscribe to their channel and enable notifications to get alerted when the stream starts.\n   - **Facebook Live**: Check the Shorty Awards\u2019 official Facebook page for live streaming options.\n   - **Twitter**: As the Shorty Awards celebrate social media excellence, they may also stream the event live on their Twitter account or utilize Twitter Moments for highlights.\n\n3. **Social Media Channels:**\n   - **Instagram and TikTok**: For behind-the-scenes content, highlights, and live updates during the event, follow the Shorty Awards\u2019 official Instagram and TikTok accounts.\n\n4. **Partner Platforms:**\n   - Occasionally, the Shorty Awards may partner with other streaming services or media outlets to broadcast parts of the event. Keep an eye on announcements leading up to the awards ceremony.\n\n5. **Post-Event Content:**\n   - If you miss the live stream, highlights, award acceptance speeches, and other segments are usually available on the Shorty Awards\u2019 YouTube channel and website shortly after the event concludes.\n\n6. **TV Airings (If Available):**\n   - While the Shorty Awards are not traditionally aired on major TV networks, it's a good idea to check entertainment channels like **MTV**, **E!**, or **Bravo**, which sometimes feature award show segments or related content. However, there\u2019s no guaranteed TV broadcast every year.\n\n**Tips to Stay Updated:**\n\n- **Subscribe to Newsletters**: Sign up for the Shorty Awards newsletter on their website to receive updates and viewing instructions.\n- **Follow Official Accounts**: Follow the Shorty Awards on all major social media platforms to get real-time updates and links to the live stream.\n- **Check Event Calendars**: Closer to the event date, media outlets and entertainment websites may provide additional information on how to watch the ceremony.\n\nBy utilizing these resources, you should be able to enjoy the Shorty Awards live from the comfort of your home. Always refer to the official Shorty Awards channels for the most accurate and up-to-date information.",
